txt.en: Corcur have begun to invade Nan Tornaeth, in the Trollshaws.\n\nWhile in Nan Tornaeth, you should drive out the Corcur who have come to the Trollshaws to reclaim their lands of old.
The Corcur, descendants of Hill-men of Rhudaur, have come down out of Angmar, seeking to reclaim their lands of old at the bidding of the Dark Lord.
Corcur have begun to invade Nan Tornaeth, in the Trollshaws.\n\nWhile in Nan Tornaeth, you should drive out the Corcur who have come to the Trollshaws to reclaim their lands of old.
